mosinstall.name: MOStlyCE
mosinstall.author: Chad Auld
mosinstall.description:
MOStlyContent Editor - The default WYSIWYG editor for Mambo, based on Moxiecode's TinyMCE!, TinyMCPUK, and the old mosCE addon.

Features:

All the features of TinyMCE by Moxiecode. It also offers dynamic plugin loading, an experimental spellchecker, an image / file manager plugin, editor compression, etc.

Important Note: Since you have installed the MOStlyCE Mambot we would also recommend you install the MOStlyCE Admin Component. This component allows you to customize the MOStlyCE editor and control its options.
